<template>
  <PortfolioList
    title="摄影作品"
    description="分享精彩摄影作品，记录美好瞬间"
    type="photo"
    :categories="photoCategories"
    :menu-groups="photoMenuGroups"
  />
</template>

<script setup>
import PortfolioList from '@/components/portfolio/PortfolioList.vue'

const photoCategories = [
  { id: 'all', name: '全部' },
  {
    id: 'portrait',
    name: '人像摄影',
    children: [
      { id: 'fashion', name: '时尚写真' },
      { id: 'life', name: '生活写真' },
      { id: 'wedding', name: '婚纱摄影' }
    ]
  },
  {
    id: 'commercial',
    name: '商业摄影',
    children: [
      { id: 'product', name: '产品摄影' },
      { id: 'food', name: '美食摄影' },
      { id: 'realestate', name: '地产摄影' }
    ]
  },
  {
    id: 'landscape',
    name: '风光摄影',
    children: [
      { id: 'nature', name: '自然风光' },
      { id: 'city', name: '城市风光' },
      { id: 'architecture', name: '建筑摄影' }
    ]
  }
]

const photoMenuGroups = [
  {
    title: '摄影分类',
    items: photoCategories.map(category => ({
      name: category.name,
      path: `/portfolio/photo?category=${category.id}`,
      icon: category.id === 'all' ? HomeIcon :
            category.id === 'portrait' ? UserGroupIcon :
            category.id === 'commercial' ? CameraIcon :
            PhotoIcon
    }))
  }
]
</script>
